def has_ironing_board_in_bathroom(room:item):
    # Check if an ironing board is inside a specified room
    symbol has_ironing_board=exists o: item : is_ironing_board(o) and inside(o, room)

def has_iron_in_bathroom(room:item):

    symbol has_iron=exists o: item : is_iron(o) and inside(o, room)
    return has_iron

        # Assume pants have to be clean before ironing
        assert clean(pants)
        achieve plugged(iron)
        achieve is_on(iron)
        achieve close_char(char, pants)
        achieve_once inhand(pants)

        foreach board: item:

        achieve unplugged(iron)
        achieve is_off(iron)
